OL,3,CTV-related anniversaries for 23 FEB
OL,4,CPROGRAMMES
OL,5,
OL,6,CG2012FHRH The Princess Royal
OL,7,Fofficially opens the new Blue Peter
OL,8,Fgarden, with presenters Barney Harwood
OL,9,Fand Helen Skelton, outside the
OL,10,Fprogramme's new studios at Media City
OL,11,FUK in Salford. The bronze statue of
OL,12,FPetra, the show's first pet, was moved
OL,13,Ffrom the old garden at Television
OL,14,FCentre. A statue of Mabel (another of
OL,15,Fthe show's longest-serving pet dogs)
OL,16,Fwas moved to the reception area along
OL,17,Fwith a sculpture of the Blue Peter ship
OL,18,Flogo.
